results.name: Theta series of A*_7 lattice. Expansion of F_8(q^2).
reference: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. 114.
link: G. C. Greubel, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
S. Ahlgren, The sixth, eighth, ninth and tenth powers of Ramanujan's theta function, Proc. Amer. Math. Soc., 128 (1999), 1333-1338.
G. Nebe and N. J. A. Sloane, Home page for this lattice
mathematica: terms = 81; phi[q_] := EllipticTheta[3, 0, q]; psi[q_] := (1/2)*q^(-1/8) * EllipticTheta[2, 0, q^(1/2)]; F8[q_] := (1/8) (phi[q^2]^7 + (2 Sqrt[q] psi[q^4])^7 + 14 phi[q^2]^5 phi[q]^2 - 7 phi[q^2]^3 phi[q]^4); s = Simplify[Normal[F8[q^2] + O[q]^terms], q>0]; CoefficientList[s, q][[1 ;; terms]] (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Jul 04 2017 *)
